      "span_text": "Note however that this would require a more sophisticated indicator, as in, and research on breakdown criteria between kinetic and Navier-Stokes regimes is still active, unless one settles for one of the standard indicators that actually measure the distance between the distribution function and its corresponding equilibrium."
